---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import LegacyHeader from '../components/LegacyHeader.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import ContactSection from '../components/ContactSection.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import ButtonPrimary from '../components/ButtonPrimary.astro';
import ButtonSecondary from '../components/ButtonSecondary.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="AI Search Optimization Services Philippines | GEO & AEO | Bright Forge SEO" description="Dominate AI-powered search results in the Philippines with our comprehensive AI Search Optimization services. We combine GEO and AEO strategies to position your brand in ChatGPT, Google AI Overviews, Perplexity, featured snippets, and voice search.">
  <LegacyHeader slot="header" />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <Hero
    badgeIcon="fas fa-brain"
    badgeText="AI Search Specialists"
    title="AI Search Optimization Services Philippines"
    breadcrumbCurrent="AI Search Optimization Philippines"
  >
    <Fragment slot="story">
      <p>Dominate the Future of Search with GEO & AEO Combined</p>

      <p>The search landscape has fundamentally transformed. Users no longer just search—they ask questions and expect instant, authoritative answers from AI assistants, voice devices, and generative platforms. If your business isn't optimized for this new reality, you're becoming invisible.</p>

      <p>Our AI Search Optimization services combine the power of Generative Engine Optimization (GEO) and Answer Engine Optimization (AEO) to ensure your business appears wherever users seek information—whether it's ChatGPT, Google AI Overviews, Perplexity, featured snippets, or voice search.</p>

      <p>As your trusted <strong>AI Search Optimization partner in the Philippines</strong>, we position your brand as the definitive answer source across all AI-powered platforms, so you can capture visibility and traffic from the rapidly growing segment of AI-driven search behaviour.</p>
