    <Fragment slot="actions">
      <ButtonPrimary href="/contact/" text="Get Your Free AI Search Audit" />
      <ButtonSecondary href="#why-ai-search" text="Learn About AI Search" />
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="visual">
      <div class="hero-image-container">
        <div class="ai-icon-grid">
          <div class="ai-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="ai-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="ai-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-microphone"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="ai-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-comments"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="ai-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-network-wired"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="ai-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Fragment>
  </Hero>

  <!-- Why AI Search Matters Section -->
  <section class="challenges-section" id="why-ai-search">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">The Shift</div>
        <h2>Why AI Search Optimization Matters <span>Now in the Philippines</span></h2>
        <p>Over 40% of searches now involve AI-powered answers, and this figure climbs monthly. The businesses that adapt will dominate; those that don't will disappear.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="challenges-content">
        <div class="challenge-text">
          <p>When someone in the Philippines asks ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Google's AI for "Who provides [your service] in [your location]?", you need to be in that response.</p>

          <p>Traditional SEO optimises for search engine results pages. AI Search Optimization goes further—ensuring your content appears in AI-generated answers, featured snippets, voice search results, and zero-click searches.</p>

          <p>Are you experiencing any of these challenges?</p>

          <ul class="challenges-list">
            <li>Your competitors consistently appear in featured snippets and AI-generated responses.</li>
            <li>Your website traffic has plateaued despite your SEO efforts.</li>
            <li>Your brand is invisible on voice search platforms like Google Assistant, Siri, and Alexa.</li>
            <li>You feel unprepared for the impact of AI Overviews and generative AI search.</li>
          </ul>

          <p><strong>If you're not thinking about how AI interprets your content, you're already behind competitors who are.</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="challenge-image">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1677442136019-21780ecad995?w=800&q=80" alt="AI Search and Generative Engine Optimization" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Two-Pillar Approach Section -->
  <section class="edge-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">Our Strategy</div>
        <h2>The Two Pillars of <span>AI Search Optimization</span></h2>
        <p>We've combined the power of GEO and AEO into a comprehensive strategy that covers every aspect of AI-powered search visibility.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillars-grid">
        <div class="pillar-card geo-pillar">
          <div class="pillar-header">
            <div class="pillar-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Generative Engine Optimization (GEO)</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="pillar-description">Optimizes your content for AI-powered generative platforms that synthesize and cite sources in their responses.</p>
          <div class="pillar-targets">
            <span class="target-badge"><i class="fas fa-comment-dots"></i> ChatGPT</span>
            <span class="target-badge"><i class="fas fa-google"></i> Google AI Overviews</span>
            <span class="target-badge"><i class="fas fa-search"></i> Perplexity</span>
            <span class="target-badge"><i class="fas fa-robot"></i> Claude & Other AI</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="pillar-benefits">
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Get cited in AI-generated responses</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Build authority signals AI models recognize</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Structure content for AI interpretation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="pillar-card aeo-pillar">
          <div class="pillar-header">
            <div class="pillar-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-microphone"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Answer Engine Optimization (AEO)</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="pillar-description">Makes your content the direct, authoritative answer for featured snippets, voice search, and zero-click results.</p>
          <div class="pillar-targets">
            <span class="target-badge"><i class="fas fa-star"></i> Featured Snippets</span>
            <span class="target-badge"><i class="fas fa-microphone"></i> Voice Search</span>
            <span class="target-badge"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> People Also Ask</span>
            <span class="target-badge"><i class="fas fa-project-diagram"></i> Knowledge Graph</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="pillar-benefits">
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Dominate "Position Zero" in search</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Become the voice search answer</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Win zero-click searches</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What's Included Section -->
  <section class="solution-section-new">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">What's Included</div>
        <h2>Your Complete <span>AI Search Optimization Solution</span></h2>
        <p>At Bright Forge SEO, we've developed a comprehensive methodology to position our clients in the Philippines as industry leaders across all AI search platforms.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="process-grid-ai">
        <div class="process-box-ai orange-bg">
          <div class="process-number-ai">1</div>
          <div class="process-icon-ai">
            <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>AI Search Audit & Strategy</h3>
          <p>We analyse how your content performs across AI platforms—ChatGPT, Google AI Overviews, Perplexity, featured snippets, and voice search. We identify gaps where competitors appear instead of you and develop a comprehensive optimization strategy.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box-ai white-bg">
          <div class="process-number-ai">2</div>
          <div class="process-icon-ai">
            <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Conversational Query Research</h3>
          <p>We move beyond basic keywords to uncover the specific questions, phrases, and natural language queries your customers use in voice and AI search. This allows us to create content that directly matches user intent.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box-ai orange-bg">
          <div class="process-number-ai">3</div>
          <div class="process-icon-ai">
            <i class="fas fa-cogs"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Technical Implementation</h3>
          <p>Advanced structured data enhancement, schema markup optimization (FAQPage, HowTo, Speakable), and site architecture adjustments to improve AI crawlability and interpretation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box-ai white-bg">
          <div class="process-number-ai">4</div>
          <div class="process-icon-ai">
            <i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3><a href="/content-seo-services-philippines/">Content Optimization for AI</a></h3>
          <p>We retrofit your existing high-value content for AI citation potential and develop new content designed to answer complex, conversational queries—structured for both human readers and AI interpretation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box-ai orange-bg">
          <div class="process-number-ai">5</div>
          <div class="process-icon-ai">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>AI Platform Monitoring</h3>
          <p>Ongoing tracking of how your business appears in responses from major AI platforms and traditional SERP features, with monthly reporting on visibility improvements across all channels.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box-ai white-bg">
          <div class="process-number-ai">6</div>
          <div class="process-icon-ai">
            <i class="fas fa-trophy"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Citation & Snippet Optimization</h3>
          <p>Strategic content development focused on becoming the most cited source in your industry for AI responses while simultaneously winning featured snippets and voice search results.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits Section -->
  <section class="benefits-section-new">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">Results</div>
        <h2>The Benefits of <span>AI Search Optimization</span></h2>
        <p>Investing in AI Search Optimization delivers powerful returns by positioning you at the forefront of how people find information.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="benefits-layout-new">
        <div class="benefits-visual-new">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?w=800&q=80"
            alt="AI Search Optimization benefits and results"
            class="benefits-image-new"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="benefits-grid-new">
          <div class="benefit-card-new">
            <div class="benefit-icon-new">
              <i class="fas fa-trophy"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Dominate AI Responses</h3>
            <p>Be the business that AI platforms cite and recommend when users ask questions in your industry.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="benefit-card-new">
            <div class="benefit-icon-new">
              <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Win Position Zero</h3>
            <p>Secure featured snippets and People Also Ask boxes—the most prominent positions in traditional search.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="benefit-card-new">
            <div class="benefit-icon-new">
              <i class="fas fa-microphone"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Own Voice Search</h3>
            <p>Become the audible answer on Google Assistant, Siri, Alexa, and other voice-activated platforms.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="benefit-card-new">
            <div class="benefit-icon-new">
              <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Future-Proof Visibility</h3>
            <p>Stay ahead as search continues evolving toward AI and natural language processing.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Timeline Section -->
  <section class="timeline-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">Timeline</div>
        <h2>What You Can <span>Expect</span></h2>
        <p>AI Search Optimization, like traditional SEO, requires sustained effort. But the businesses that invest now will dominate AI search results for years whilst competitors scramble to catch up.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-grid">
        <div class="timeline-card">
          <div class="timeline-period">1-3 Months</div>
          <h3>Foundation</h3>
          <p>Technical implementation, initial content optimisation, baseline measurement of current AI visibility, and quick wins on featured snippet opportunities.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-card">
          <div class="timeline-period">3-6 Months</div>
          <h3>Growth</h3>
          <p>Increasing appearances in AI-generated responses, measurable growth in featured snippets, improved voice search positioning, and competitive gains.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-card">
          <div class="timeline-period">6-12 Months</div>
          <h3>Dominance</h3>
          <p>Dominant presence in AI responses for key topics, established authority across platforms, and consistent citation advantage over competitors.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
  <section class="choose-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">The Difference</div>
        <h2>Why Choose <span>Bright Forge SEO?</span></h2>
        <p class="subtitle">Your AI Search Optimization Experts in the Philippines</p>
      </div>

      <div class="choose-grid">
        <div class="choose-card">
          <div class="choose-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-flask"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Proven Testing & Refinement</h3>
          <p>Most agencies are still figuring out AI optimization. We've been testing and refining AI search strategies for over two years, tracking which techniques actually move the needle versus which are theoretical.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="choose-card">
          <div class="choose-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>15+ Years SEO Expertise</h3>
          <p>Our approach combines 15+ years of proven SEO expertise with cutting-edge AI platform knowledge. We understand how search engines work and how AI models process information, make recommendations, and cite sources.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="choose-card">
          <div class="choose-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Data-Driven Approach</h3>
          <p>Our strategies are built on meticulous research, competitor analysis, and performance data—not guesswork. Every recommendation is backed by data, and every report shows measurable improvement.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="choose-card">
          <div class="choose-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-map-marked-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Philippines Market Focus</h3>
          <p>We understand the unique needs of businesses in the Philippines, ensuring your AI Search Optimization strategy is tailored for both local and global visibility.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Investment Section -->
  <section class="investment-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">Investment</div>
        <h2>Investment & <span>Terms</span></h2>
      </div>

      <div class="investment-content">
        <div class="investment-card">
          <div class="investment-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-dollar-sign"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Starting Investment</h3>
          <p>AI Search Optimization services start at <strong>16 hours monthly ($480 USD at $30/hour)</strong> for comprehensive GEO and AEO optimization and monitoring.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="investment-card">
          <div class="investment-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Commitment</h3>
          <p>Given the strategic nature of the work and time required to influence AI platform behaviour, we require a <strong>minimum six-month commitment</strong>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="investment-card">
          <div class="investment-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>What's Included</h3>
          <p>Strategy development, technical implementation, content optimisation for AI platforms, and comprehensive monthly reporting on AI visibility metrics.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">FAQ</div>
        <h2>Frequently Asked <span>Questions</span></h2>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What is the difference between GEO and AEO?</h3>
          <p>Generative Engine Optimization (GEO) focuses on AI-powered generative platforms like ChatGPT, Google AI Overviews, and Perplexity—ensuring your content gets cited in AI responses. Answer Engine Optimization (AEO) targets traditional answer features like featured snippets, voice search, and Knowledge Graph. Our AI Search Optimization combines both for complete coverage.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
