          <p>Initial visibility improvements can appear within 1-3 months for technical implementations and featured snippets. Meaningful AI citations typically emerge at 3-6 months, with dominant positioning achieved at 6-12 months. AI platforms update continuously, so consistent optimization is essential.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Is AI Search Optimization relevant for my industry?</h3>
          <p>Absolutely. Any industry where customers ask questions and seek recommendations can benefit. Whether you're in e-commerce, professional services, healthcare, or B2B, positioning yourself for AI citations and featured snippets provides a significant competitive advantage.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Will AI Search Optimization replace traditional SEO?</h3>
          <p>No, AI Search Optimization complements traditional SEO. A strong technical foundation, quality backlinks, and excellent user experience remain crucial. AI Search Optimization is an essential layer on top of solid SEO that prepares you for the future of search.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="cta-container">
        <h2>Ready to Dominate AI Search Results in the Philippines?</h2>
        <p>The businesses that optimise for AI search now will have an insurmountable advantage over those who wait. Your competitors are either already investing in AI Search Optimization or will be within months. Don't get left behind.</p>
        <a href="/contact/" class="cta-button">Get Your Free AI Search Audit</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <ContactSection />

